
- Requirements:

  - A C++ compiler with C++14 support.
    The following compiler has been tested:
    - GCC 5.4 (Linux x86_64).

  - Qt 5 (tested with version 5.6.1).

  - PortAudio with C++ binding (tested with version v19_20140130).

  - JACK Audio Connection Kit (tested with version 1.9.10).

  - FFTW - single precision (tested with version 3.3.4).

  - GamaTTS (use the latest version).

  - GamaTTS:Interactive (use the latest version).
    The source must be in ../gama_tts_interactive.

- Generate the Makefile:

  qmake
  # or
  qmake "INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr"

- Build:

  make

  # Optional (Linux):
  make install
  # or
  make install INSTALL_ROOT=/tmp/install
